data.description: Crawley-This fabulous 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 story home on 3 level acres offers a spacious open floor plan for a great entertaining space or large family gathering. A well equipped oak kitchen with granite counters, all stainless steel appliances that convey. Shiny oak hardwood floors in the kitchen and  dining room. The dining area is open to the living area and a main level office space/family room. The upstairs master suite and bath is a great retreat. Large covered rear deck with amazing views. A 2 car attached garage with storage area. Neat, clean and move in ready with lots of rooms for a growing family. Conveniently located just 5 minutes from I64 between Beckley and Lewisburg.
